17:41.160 --> 17:42.280
Zhi Zhi.

17:42.360 --> 17:43.200
Ibu.

17:43.680 --> 17:44.760
Kau sedang di mana?

17:45.880 --> 17:46.840
Aku di…

17:47.640 --> 17:48.960
Aku di… Ibu lihat.

17:49.040 --> 17:50.360
Kenapa seperti…

17:51.280 --> 17:52.280
