17:52.360 --> 17:53.400
Benar!

17:53.480 --> 17:54.640
Aku sedang kamping.

17:55.520 --> 17:56.560
Nyaman sekali.

17:57.160 --> 17:58.520
Kau sedang kamping?

17:59.160 --> 18:00.320
